cards.description:
AMIE Locations - Farallon
Design summary

> Addresses
	Model Address as a semanitic node (E45 Address) 
	Locations (top node of bracnch) P87_is_identified_by Addresses


> Description
	Includes directions


> Property Ownership (Cadastral Reference)
	Modeled as E42 Identifier because parcel identifiers are meant to uniquely and permanently refere to a specifc area of land ownership


> Admin/Related Areas
	Modeled as E53 Place
	Locations (top node of branch) P121_overlaps_with Adminstrative/Related Areas

	Used to manage:
		Admin area
		Geopolitical areas
		Localities
		Other areas (such as zoning, special use, archaeological research areas)


> Map References
	Modeled as E44 Place_Appellation
	Locations (top node of branch) P1_is_identified_by Map References

	Used to manage 
		National Grid References
		Map sheets
